    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lover! Up for grabs is my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing this beauty than I care to admit, and honestly, she still looks like she just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been strictly garage-kept and pampered since day one. There\u2019s one tiny, barely-there mark on the rear rim that you\u2019d need a magnifying glass to find, but other than that, she\u2019s absolute perfection on wheels. I\u2019m only letting her go to a home that will appreciate her as much as I have. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
