    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine a vehicle that doesn't just transport you, but transcends the very notion of travel. This masterpiece is a silent sentinel of elegance, finished in a coat of paint so deep and lustrous it feels like peering into the heart of a sapphire. Within the cabin, the air is thick with the rich, heady aroma of preserved leather, each stitch a testament to a bygone era of craftsmanship. It glides through the world with a grace that turns heads and stills hearts\u2014a rare specimen that has been shielded from the vulgarity of the road and kept in a state of suspended animation. To own this is to own a piece of history, a pristine sanctuary of power and poise that awaits its next great chapter.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
